{{Infobox language |name=Tefaro |nativename= |region=[[Indonesia]]n [[Papua (Indonesian province)|Papua]] |speakers=100 |date=1987 |ref = e18 |familycolor=Papuan |fam1=[[East Geelvink Bay languages|East Geelvink Bay]]? |fam2= |iso3=tfo |glotto=tefa1238 |glottorefname=Tefaro }} '''Tefaro''' is a [[Papuan language]] of the [[Indonesia]]n province of [[Papua (province)|Papua]], on the eastern shore of [[Cenderawasih Bay]].
